(5, 'homeAbout', 6, '103', 'Welcome to IIA Group <span>A group for Quality AME training</span>', 'IIA Group was established in the year 1981 and the foundation stone was laid by Capt. R.N. Sinha. He was\n            also\n            the founder chairman of Aviators Co-operative, the pioneer operator to start non-scheduled MRO (Maintenance\n            Repair\n            Organization) operations in the year 1968. The time when working on aircraft and helicopters was a mere\n            dream for\n            the student, IIA Group was amongst the first in India to set up an Aircraft Maintenance Engineering training\n            institute. Thus IIA Group has been producing world-class Aircraft Maintenance Engineers for last 37\n            years.<br><br>\n            When a good science laboratory in a college was considered an achievement, IIA Group brought in aircraft â€“\n            Heavy\n            pressurized Aircraft Hawker HS â€“ 125, Learjet â€“ 24, Bonanza A â€“ 35, Helicopter SA â€“ 318C, Eurocopter EC â€“\n            120B â€“\n            for practical training of students. IIA Group contributed significantly in shaping up technical jobs and\n            careers\n            in Indian Aviation Industry.<br><br>Many of our alumni have now served for decades in the global aviation\n            scenario. They hold very high positions in the aviation industry. We are pioneers and leaders for creating\n            world-class Aircraft Maintenance Engineers (AME) leaving our competitors far behind as more than 50% of the\n            technical workforce in the industry come from our group. These are the people who would interview you when\n            you\n            pass out from one of our colleges and step into the industry. It is our sincere endeavor to give all our\n            students\n            the best possible platform and support to help them achieve their goals and realize all their\n            dreams.<br><br>\n\n            Milestone We are