(10, 'courses', 11, NULL, '<strong>DGCA</strong> APPROVED<br>COURSES', 'DGCA', '<p>Aircraft Maintenance Engineering (AME) is a job profile with high dignity and a great sense of responsibility. Owing to the strict standards of safety and security, the entire course towards AME licenses is governed by the Directorate General of Civil Aviation (DGCA), Govt. of India.</p>', ' <a href=\"dgca\" class=\"btn\">Know More</a>', 'Courses Offered', 'odd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-08-28 14:59:31', '2020-08-17 12:28:49'),
